            <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2 leading-6">
            Wedding Transportation & Shuttle Services
            </h3>

            <p class="text-sm leading-snug font-light">
            JDK Transportation's wedding shuttles handle transportation so you can focus on the celebration. Personalized bus rentals for pickups, transfers, and late-night rides in India. Timely arrivals and safe rides home – we've got logistics covered.
